DOC.TE:
   Higazy, dressed in a blue prison uniform, sat quietly in court Friday
while his bail was argued. A U.S. marshal towered over the slight,
dark-haired defendant.

   Missing are Steve Coulombe, 38, of Agua Dulce, the company's owner;
Nelson Ray Brinkman, 30, an assistant engine builder from Phelan; and
Chuck Wiseman, 47, a customer and Coulombe's friend.

